    "frontNotes": "<p data-path-to-node=\"0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">هذه الجملة صيغت في زمن <b data-path-to-node=\"0\" data-index-in-node=\"23\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">الحاضر (Le présent de l'indicatif)</b>.</p><hr data-path-to-node=\"1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><h3 data-path-to-node=\"2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">توضيح التركيبة والقواعد:</h3><ul data-path-to-node=\"3\" style=\"padding-inline-start: 32px; font-family: &quot;Google Sans Text&quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><li style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><p data-path-to-node=\"3,0,0\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"3,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">vais</b>: هو تصريف فعل <b data-path-to-node=\"3,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"19\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">aller</b> (يذهب) في زمن الحاضر مع الضمير (<span class=\"math-inline\" data-math=\"Je\" data-index-in-node=\"57\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">$Je$</span>). وهو فعل من المجموعة الثالثة غير المنتظمة.</p></li><li style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><p data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">au</b>: حرف جر مركب وأصله (<span class=\"math-inline\" data-math=\"à + le\" data-index-in-node=\"23\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">$à + le$</span>)، حيث يُدمج حرف الجر <span class=\"math-inline\" data-math=\"à\" data-index-in-node=\"51\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">$à$</span> مع أداة التعريف المذكرة <span class=\"math-inline\" data-math=\"le\" data-index-in-node=\"77\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">$le$</span> ليصبحا <b data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"87\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">au</b> أمام الاسم المذكر المفرد <b data-path-to-node=\"3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"115\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">travail</b> (العمل).</p></li><li style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><p data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">en voiture</b>: تعبير يعني \"بالسيارة\". استخدمنا حرف الجر <b data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"53\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">en</b> هنا لأنه يُستخدم مع وسائل النقل المغلقة التي ندخل في جوفها (مثل: <i data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"121\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">en voiture</i>, <i data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"133\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">en train</i>, <i data-path-to-node=\"3,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"143\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">en bus</i>).</p></li></ul>",
