t: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">avoir</b> في الزمن الحاضر مع الضمير (<span class=\"math-inline\" data-math=\"Je\" data-index-in-node=\"60\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">$Je$</span>).</p></li><li style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><p data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">oublié</b>: هو اسم المفعول (Le participe passé) للفعل <b data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"50\" style=\"line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;\">oublier</b> (ينسى).</p></li></ul>",
